column5: Leaving for the big lake this weekend, any new reports out there! Thx everyone!
fishing has been excellent. 12-15 feet of water
What part of lac seul are you fishing?
Northwest part of Lac Seul. McKenzie Bay, South Inlet and Bay of Islands, Thx
Our group is heading up this Saturday staying at Fisherman's Cove. It sounds like the weather is going to really nice.
fishing has been excellent all over west side of lac seul mckenzie bay poplar narrows ghost narrows manitoba point shanty narrows all doing very well
